highlights.text: “Babblarnas vaggvisa” by Babblarna has been on Top Songs Sweden the longest, at 1717 days straight.
“TAKEDOWN (JEONGYEON, JIHYO, CHAEYOUNG) (from the Netflix film KPop Demon Hunters)” by TWICE is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Sweden, up 87 spots at #68.
Hov1 has the most spots on Top Songs Sweden. “Räddare i nöden” is the highest at #9.
“LOVE SONG” by Justin Bieber is the highest new entry on Top Songs Sweden at #103.
